title: 1 bedroom Douglass Park $950
posting_body: ['Hi Everyone!', 'The apartment is a one bedroom with one bathroom on the second floor.', 'The apartment has been recently completely renovated.', 'Located two blocks from Douglas Park and less than a block from the Kedzie Pink line.', 'Close to Cermak and Kedzie.', 'There is a laundromat three blocks away.', "There is a Pete's and Cermak Produce that is close to the apartment.", 'The location of the apartment is close to Pilsen and Little Village.', 'We live in a quiet block.', 'To get a lease; it is a $475 move in fee and first-month rent, no evictions, and income must be twice the rent and a 600 credit score.', 'The building is also smoke-free and there is a backyard and plenty of free parking.', 'One more perk is that residents of Douglas Park receive free Riotfest tickets.']
